### Testing Service Integration

```bash
# 1. Start Auth Service
cd microservices/auth-service
npm run dev

# 2. Test integration endpoint
curl http://localhost:7020/api/v1/integration/health

# 3. Test token validation (requires service API key)
curl -X POST http://localhost:7020/api/v1/integration/validate-token \
  -H "X-Service-Key: 29188e760a4166559cf35f8f60df08fdec190055397bace0e776ec803821230f" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"token":"<jwt-token>"}'
```

